<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmed - TagBreak</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #1e4941;
            color: #e3bcae;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(227, 188, 174, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid rgba(227, 188, 174, 0.3);
        }
        
        .logo-placeholder {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #e3bcae;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #f5d5c8;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #e3bcae;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .message-box {
            background-color: rgba(227, 188, 174, 0.08);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid rgba(227, 188, 174, 0.15);
        }
        
        .message-box p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .message-box p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            color: #f5d5c8;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #d4a798;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .brand {
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #f5d5c8;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(227, 188, 174, 0.3), transparent);
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.9rem;
            }
            
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-placeholder">TB</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1>Your Break Starts Now</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Order successfully placed!</p>
        
        <div class="divider"></div>
        
        <div class="message-box">
            <p>Thank you for your purchase! Your order has been successfully requested and is being processed.</p>
            <p>This is a <span class="highlight">once-only batch item</span>. We use a request-to-purchase step to ensure everything stays genuine and safe for each of our buyers.</p>
            <p>You'll receive a confirmation email shortly with your order details.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Have a wonderful day! :)</p>
            <p>Team <span class="brand">TagBreak</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>